    {
      "text": "Dragon Ball Z: Gekitou Tenkaichi Budoukai is the first fighting video game based on Dragon Ball Z. The game was unique in that it came with a special card reader attachment, the Datach Joint Rom System, which requires several special cards to be swiped in order to add characters and items in the game.",
